Dialog.notes: Subject's death throws, then husking. 3-5 seconds.
Addressing his captors. Voice is more distant, thru a speaker.

Dialog.text: I have a daughter. They took me from her.
I was promised I would see her again. I signed your papers.
Dialog.notes: He knows he's doomed. Shaming them for what they are about to do.

Dialog.text: Your family. You must hate them very much to do this. I hear it in your voices.
Look at me. Look at the man you are killing.
What you do, kills us both.
